## 2026-03-27 - moveGroup doesn't check for path collisions in target set
- Added collision detection before moving tokens in both `moveGroup` and `moveToken` methods.
- `moveGroup`: For empty groups, checks if `groupPath` exists in target. For leaf tokens, collects all conflicting paths and throws a descriptive error listing up to 5 collisions.
- `moveToken`: Checks if `tokenPath` exists in target before beginning the batch operation.

